AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-V%C4%83n-th%E1%BB%ABa-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng/poem-F5IDMjeyDpyOfAjIQxJRYg">Độ Hoài hữu cảm Văn thừa tướng - 渡淮有感文丞將</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/H%E1%BB%93ng-l%C3%A2u-m%E1%BB%99ng-d%E1%BA%ABn-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-4BBjszuacCHWN-ao9r7yzQ">Hồng lâu mộng dẫn tử - 紅樓夢引子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/M%C3%B4-ng%C6%B0-nhi/poem-kotueSADUs76XWra40hfkQ">Mô ngư nhi - 摸魚兒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Ti%E1%BB%85n-tr%C3%AD-s%E1%BB%B1-kinh-do%C3%A3n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-Tr%E1%BB%A9/poem-NrIIAlUplVGXQz8y0KLfkA">Tiễn trí sự kinh doãn Nguyễn Công Trứ - 餞致事京尹阮公著</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BA%A1c-mi%E1%BA%BFu-to%E1%BA%A1i-t%C3%BAc-nh%E1%BA%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-m%C3%B4n-l%C3%A2u/poem-Fi0Gv61h-zHA0H8Q_95dwg">Yết Hành nhạc miếu toại túc nhạc tự đề môn lâu - 謁衡岳廟遂宿嶽寺題門樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
